BAGGAGE-Per passenger, two pieces of checked baggage,
total length, width, and height of each not to exceed 62 inches
(157 cm), total legnth, width, and height of both combined not to
exceed 107 inches (272 cm).
EXCESS BAGGAGE CHARGES-In
excess
baggage
allowance or oversized baggage, $10.00 per piece, on a space

BAGGAGE LIABILITY—$750.00 per passenger; all baggage
claims must be submitted immediately.

flammable

CHECK IN TIME-Passengers must be checked in at least ten

reservation may be cancelled.

ARRIVAL,

CREDIT CARDS-SFO Helicopter Airlines accepts American
Express, Diners Club, Carte Blanche, MasterCard, VISA and
UATP.
TICKETING —Tickets may be purchased from your travel agent,
corporate traffic manager, any scheduled airline, or any SFO

connect with a United flight: 50 minutes for all other airlines.
